Package alternativevoting

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlternativeElection
    Provides methods for running each round of eliminating a candidate.
    backend
    Provides backend support for tables.
    BallotStats
    Provides ballot statistics.
    BarChart
    Provides a way to draw a bar chart for candidates.
    Candidate
    The Candidate class supplies the basic fields needed to define a candidate and modify a candidate's vote count.
    delete
    The delete class deletes tables from the backend.
    FinalActionButtons
    The FinalActionButtons class allows certain actions to be performed on a ResultScreen.
    heroku
    Heroku queries from a database and returns relevant information.
    JUAlternativeVotingTest
    Tests Alternative Election, Candidate, and BallotStats classes with JUnit tests.
    Result
    Creates a ResultScreen object.
    ResultScreen
    Creates a ResultScreen object.
